You can see <a href="pubs.html">a list of my publications</a> 
with many of them online.  My general area of research is that of database
theory.

<p>

<a href="talks.html">Slides of some of my talks</a> may be online...

<p>

My doctoral advisor was <a
  href="http://alpha.uhasselt.be/jan.vandenbussche/jp/">Jan
  Paredaens</a>.
My own doctoral students are
